{"tid":1639700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"希拉莉：每一個美國人都有權利去聲援香港人爭取民主與人權","createTime":"2019-10-08T16:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T17:17:04.000Z","uid":53369,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"05d492683f98b798bcedeebb16bb3dbe60d8685f","tid":1639700,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFeFoos.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFeFoos.png&h=83d501b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hillaryclinton/status/1181599014434811905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhillaryclinton%2Fstatus%2F1181599014434811905&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=3caf42e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhillaryclinton%2Fstatus%2F1181599014434811905&h=d27565aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hillaryclinton/status/1181599014434811905</a>"},{"pid":"e7308ae8ea5c99479f540114ad3b1c0a09e041d7","tid":1639700,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:44:11.000Z","msg":"加強文宣<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"084d04ea371e74b975894c3025dbb5115f345388","tid":1639700,"uid":129309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05d492683f98b798bcedeebb16bb3dbe60d8685f","tid":1639700,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFeFoos.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFeFoos.png&h=83d501b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hillaryclinton/status/1181599014434811905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhillaryclinton%2Fstatus%2F1181599014434811905&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=3caf42e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhillaryclinton%2Fstatus%2F1181599014434811905&h=d27565aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hillaryclinton/status/1181599014434811905</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"真正的政客出來了, 唔割"},{"pid":"a88ac5dff8da7343ee79c203992d21812451c39b","tid":1639700,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:46:18.000Z","msg":"Connect埋呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e96504a51d367a4ae0f8d7b31b0cf03c1a4d4c","tid":1639700,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n777仲connect埋全美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 